Various Aspects of the Inner Life — The Law of Life
I would cease from all my strife—
‘Tis not I but He who worketh—
As I rest and reign in life.
Law of life in Christ has freed me
From the law of sin and death,
As I walk in Christ, in spirit,
As the law, He’s now dispensing
Making me a man of life.
Now this law is shaping me.
